data.description: Fontana living at its finest.  Located a few miles from Victoria Gardens and shopping centers, this beautiful turnkey home offers all the qualities of modern living. This home offers laminate flooring, throughout the first floor.  Just off the foyer, the downstairs master and powder room are conveniently located.  As you pass the master suite and powder room, the floor plan truly opens up with a great room featuring the kitchen, living area and dining room.  The open floor plan truly make the downstairs feel like one great room.  Upstairs you'll find the 3 bedrooms, the master suite and two other bedrooms along with a comfortable loft.  The community offers a pool and recreation room just a few houses away which includes a BBQ area and a kiddie pool.  Great for entertaining.
